                  "pageTitle": "Hata-Satya",
                  "pageId": 1527118,
                  "revisionId": 2657473,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Bonus damage instances from Toxic Lash and Xata's Whisper count as one extra hit."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
