                  "pageId": 1527118,
                  "revisionId": 2657473,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Swapping to Incarnon Form counts as reloading the Soma Prime and will therefore end the bonus."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Hata-Satya",
                  "pageId": 1527118,
                  "revisionId": 2657473,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Using melee , Parazon mercy finishers, or activating an Exalted Weapon ability are counted as holstering the Soma Prime and will therefore end the bonus."
